Package com.example.freeturilo.storage

Interface InternalConnection.Builder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StorageConnection.Builder
    Enclosing interface:
    InternalConnection
    public static interface InternalConnection.Builder
    Builder of internal connections.

    Object of class implementing this interface builds I/O connections with custom context.

    This interface should be treated as a factory for internal connections. It has been designed to support internal storage connections but could also be used for other types of I/O file-based connections (it is used with project resource files for testing purposes). For feasibility of understanding the methods will be described as if they were methods used for internal storage connections.
